      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MARGI JEAN (5) drifted back settling but did best work late to finish 5th at this track over 520m (30.50). Returns to favourable track. Rates on top in this line up. OSCAR EIGHTY ONE (4) turned in a moderate performance last time when eighth at this track over 520m behind Clifton Kuna (36.92) in a Novice race. Scored at his previous run. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Should be about the money. ERIN GO BRAGH (2) showed good pace from out wide and was prominent early but began to paddle and faded out of it when 5th at this track in Novice race company. Can measure up this time. JUST A DUKE (1) will have admirers after placing last time out.",
